node.text:
Please keep our mom in your thoughts @just_aminat 

Earlier this week, during a family bike ride, Alexis lost balance on a steep hill. Mom instincts kicked in and Ami JUMPED off the bike (it was going 20mph!) to help Alexis not fall. 

But she did fall. And hard. 
Ami also fell. Harder. 😔

See Alexis's chin? Big cut there and 2 more on her body. 
But Mom...oh my: BOTH broken wrists, lacerations, strained muscles and ligaments. A lot of pain. 🤕

She'll be ok, just not tomorrow or anytime soon. 
It's painful and her spirits are down...so please keep her @just_aminat and @mightymcclures in your thoughts. 🙏

#gratitude
